<TEXT>
<P>
 An auction of broaches made by artists, held Saturday at the Muckenthaler 
Cultural Center in Fullerton, raised about $7,000 for arts education programs 
in the Fullerton School District. Artists from Orange and Los Angeles Counties 
including Rachel Rosenthal and Janice DeLoof crafted broaches for the sale. 
</P>
