<HEADLINE>
<P>
THE TIMES FILM INDEX: DOMESTIC MARKET SHARE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Domestic market share and number of films in release for U.S. distributors 
from Jan. 3 to Oct. 2: 
</P>
<P>
 Buena Vista 
</P>
