<HEADLINE>
<P>
BRIEFCASE: RESTAURANTS AND RETAIL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
Compiled by Greg Johnson, Times staff writer 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The Lab's Poetic Celebration: The Lab, a collection of retail shops at 2930 
Bristol Ave. in Costa Mesa, will celebrate its first anniversary this weekend 
with "writings on the wall," a poetry festival featuring readings by more than 
20 Orange County poets. Proceeds from a raffle will benefit Literacy Volunteers 
of America and the Orange County Poetic Mentorship Council. 
</P>
<P>
 The poetry readings, lottery and entertainment begin at 3 p.m. on Saturday and 
Sunday. 
</P>
