<HEADLINE>
<P>
BRIEFCASE: RESTAURANTS AND RETAIL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
Compiled by Greg Johnson, Times staff writer 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Hansen Goes to Market Ecologically: Hansen Beverage Co. has introduced 
Equator, a teen-oriented line that's being marketed as an environmentally 
friendly concoction.A portion of the proceeds from Equator sales will be 
donated to Earth Day U.S.A. and cans will be marketed in a campaign that's 
