<DOCID> 085516 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
October 4, 1994, Tuesday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 1; Column 4; Metro Desk 
