</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Shuttle flights -- The Times reported incorrectly Sunday that Shuttle by 
United has begun flights at John Wayne Airport. The short-distance discount 
service, which began Saturday, flies to four other Southern California 
airports, but not John Wayne. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Correction 
</P>
